snippet.title: The Bear And The Admiral – Release Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Save the solar system, travelling through hand-drawn cartoon worlds, brimming with monsters and aliens!

The Bear And The Admiral launching October 7th 2021 on Nintendo Switch™.

Music tracks used in this trailer:
'Diary Of The Admiral'  -  by Jack Boylan 
'The Bear And The Admiral Main Theme'  -  by Miyoko Takaoka

Nintendo Switch is a trademark of Nintendo.
